Conclusion
These 28 enhancements represent a comprehensive strategy to transform Givoro from a functional MVP into a market-leading AI-powered gift recommendation platform. The recommendations are designed to work synergistically, with each enhancement amplifying the impact of others.

Key Success Metrics to Track:
Conversion Rate: Suggestions → Clicks → Purchases
Revenue Per User: Average affiliate commission per session
User Retention: Return visit rate within 30 days
AI Quality Score: User satisfaction with suggestions
System Reliability: API uptime and response time

Next Steps:
Review and prioritize enhancements based on your strategic goals
Identify any enhancements requiring clarification
Confirm technical constraints (budget, timeline, team capacity)
Begin implementation with Phase 1 quick wins